Author: SpaceWhale88
Text: I just got switched from adderall to vyvanse and effexor to pristiq. My appetite feels like that of a normal person. This week I've been eating a normal amount of food, although I did have a mini binge last night and purged but that was only because I was drunk.   My brother says I should have a depression twitter so I can turn my depression meals into viral posts.

Author: SubBiscuit
Text: > I was too worn out to even microwave a lean cuisine and ended up just getting high and eating sour patch kids  Are we the same person??  Also I hope things get better for you soon. We're all here for you <3
